1
00:00:21,184 --> 00:00:22,464
♪That day♪

2
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:24,448
♪Nothing stays together forever♪

3
00:00:24,448 --> 00:00:25,792
♪I've quit romance♪

4
00:00:26,218 --> 00:00:27,920
♪Who hasn't failed again♪

5
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:31,424
♪Crying in death♪

6
00:00:31,424 --> 00:00:34,016
♪And in life♪

7
00:00:34,432 --> 00:00:36,370
♪Even now♪

8
00:00:36,672 --> 00:00:38,656
♪We keep learning♪

9
00:00:38,656 --> 00:00:39,680
♪It's no surprise♪

10
00:00:39,744 --> 00:00:42,144
♪Being happy is so hard♪

11
00:00:42,144 --> 00:00:43,968
♪Weirdly, I became a role model♪

12
00:00:44,736 --> 00:00:46,688
♪On the day we met again, we said hi♪

13
00:00:46,688 --> 00:00:52,896
♪It was a reminder,
a test, and a complaint♪

14
00:00:52,896 --> 00:00:56,003
♪Who can do anything without regret♪

15
00:00:56,003 --> 00:00:59,424
♪I am all right♪

16
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:05,074
♪May you live in peace♪

17
00:01:05,074 --> 00:01:07,456
♪Let the world roar♪

18
00:01:07,456 --> 00:01:09,732
♪Sounds like a carnival♪

19
00:01:09,732 --> 00:01:14,453
♪Being alive is never dull♪

20
00:01:14,453 --> 00:01:18,830
♪How wonderful to be free♪

21
00:01:18,830 --> 00:01:23,485
♪I became even better without you♪

22
00:01:23,485 --> 00:01:25,824
♪Nothing can be perfect♪

23
00:01:25,824 --> 00:01:28,224
♪We bless each other in pain♪

24
00:01:28,224 --> 00:01:34,234
♪We nod and smile♪

25
00:01:35,328 --> 00:01:36,288
♪May we both be well♪

26
00:01:36,288 --> 00:01:41,024
= Love's Ambition=

27
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:11,920
=Episode 13=

28
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,960
Distinguished leaders and guests,

29
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,641
good day.

30
00:02:15,761 --> 00:02:18,401
(Strategic Cooperation Signing Ceremony)
This is the venue

31
00:02:18,481 --> 00:02:21,080
for Jinda Group and Shifeng Group's
strategic cooperation signing.

32
00:02:21,281 --> 00:02:24,281
First, let's give
a warm round of applause

33
00:02:24,401 --> 00:02:26,921
to extend our most sincere welcome
to all the leaders

34
00:02:27,041 --> 00:02:28,841
and guests present here today.

35
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,041
Welcome!

36
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,041
Alright,

37
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:38,081
now please welcome
the two representatives to the stage.

38
00:02:38,241 --> 00:02:41,320
Mr. Shen Jinsong,
Chairman of Jinda Group,

39
00:02:41,521 --> 00:02:44,200
and Mr. Zheng Yuanzhou,
Chairman of Shifeng Group,

40
00:02:44,521 --> 00:02:45,801
please come forward to sign.

41
00:02:45,961 --> 00:02:46,681
Applause please.

42
00:02:55,361 --> 00:02:55,801
Very well.

43
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:58,640
Both representatives,
please hold the ceremonial pens.

44
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,241
Three, two, one.

45
00:03:01,361 --> 00:03:02,961
Please sign the documents.

46
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,600
Hold on!

47
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,160
A moment if I may.

48
00:03:13,561 --> 00:03:14,200
Zheng Yuanzhou,

49
00:03:14,801 --> 00:03:16,480
during Shifeng Group's board election,

50
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,640
you unlawfully
obtained votes and benefits

51
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,801
through bribery, etc.

52
00:03:20,121 --> 00:03:21,801
Your actions
constitute suspected bribery.

53
00:03:23,681 --> 00:03:24,480
Here is the warrant.

54
00:03:25,681 --> 00:03:26,320
Read it.

55
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,880
Come with us for investigation.

56
00:03:29,241 --> 00:03:29,801
Cuff him.

57
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:38,640
Step aside.

58
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,841
Step aside.

59
00:03:43,841 --> 00:03:44,561
Please make way.

60
00:03:48,144 --> 00:03:49,509
(Shen)

61
00:03:50,681 --> 00:03:51,160
Mr. Shen,

62
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:54,241
the news of our impending cooperation
with Shifeng was released early.

63
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,361
When Mr. Zheng's scandal broke,

64
00:03:56,561 --> 00:03:58,681
our stock price started plummeting
at market open.

65
00:03:59,001 --> 00:04:00,961
If there's no recovery by tomorrow,

66
00:04:01,440 --> 00:04:03,920
shareholders will likely
convene an emergency board meeting.

67
00:04:06,681 --> 00:04:07,320
I see.

68
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,320
Mr. Shen.

69
00:04:12,561 --> 00:04:12,920
Dad.

70
00:04:13,081 --> 00:04:13,681
Don't call me.

71
00:04:15,361 --> 00:04:15,920
Go home.

72
00:04:19,521 --> 00:04:21,640
I came to report something important.

73
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:25,561
Zheng Yuanzhou's
bribery-fueled chairmanship election

74
00:04:26,241 --> 00:04:28,640
has destroyed his reputation.

75
00:04:29,081 --> 00:04:31,160
Shifeng Group
can't escape the fallout either.

76
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,920
Several agreed-upon projects

77
00:04:33,561 --> 00:04:36,040
are now facing withdrawal
from key partners.

78
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,920
I've decided to collaborate with Shouke

79
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,681
to reclaim those projects.

80
00:04:40,961 --> 00:04:42,081
That's preposterous!

81
00:04:42,681 --> 00:04:43,841
What's the point of that?

82
00:04:44,241 --> 00:04:44,960
We have no land.

83
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,200
Shouke and I secured it

84
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,400
through bidding.

85
00:04:51,001 --> 00:04:52,801
Land acquisition requires funds.

86
00:04:53,121 --> 00:04:54,320
Where's your money?

87
00:04:55,041 --> 00:04:56,001
Yuanhang Fund.

88
00:04:56,801 --> 00:04:57,520
Yuanhang?

89
00:05:01,921 --> 00:05:03,041
These people and affairs

90
00:05:04,241 --> 00:05:06,280
couldn't have been achieved overnight.

91
00:05:07,921 --> 00:05:10,681
Unless you had a long-term,
meticulous plan

92
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,241
already in motion.

93
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,601
Even with such a plan,

94
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:19,080
if Zheng hadn't imploded,

95
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,840
it couldn't have been executed.

96
00:05:25,921 --> 00:05:27,440
You knew Zheng's downfall?

97
00:05:30,001 --> 00:05:31,320
Dad, I warned you before.

98
00:05:31,361 --> 00:05:32,161
You forgot.

99
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,161
Zheng Yuanzhou has three confidants.

100
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:38,200
The last-ranked one is the most capable.

101
00:05:38,561 --> 00:05:39,601
He overworked

102
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:42,200
but didn't gain enough credit
for a long time.

103
00:05:42,681 --> 00:05:43,840
Resentment was inevitable.

104
00:05:48,001 --> 00:05:48,520
Wait.

105
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:49,640
Let me confirm.

106
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,361
You're implying

107
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:54,840
that you orchestrated Zheng's downfall?

108
00:05:55,721 --> 00:05:58,121
Certain truths should remain
between father and son.

109
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,880
Hold on.

110
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:01,681
Move over there.

111
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:03,481
Tell me.

112
00:06:03,801 --> 00:06:07,241
How did you secure that man's loyalty?

113
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,440
During my London internship,

114
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,041
I flew back five times.

115
00:06:13,481 --> 00:06:14,520
He avoided me each time.

116
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,161
On the sixth attempt, he met me.

117
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,161
We immediately aligned.

118
00:06:19,481 --> 00:06:20,960
All terms were agreed upon.

119
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:24,640
I emphasized three points:

120
00:06:25,921 --> 00:06:26,640
recognition,

121
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:28,280
sincerity,

122
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,601
and benefits.

123
00:06:30,561 --> 00:06:33,241
I showed him my character
and convinced him

124
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,960
that when I pursue goals,

125
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:39,400
I spare no effort to achieve them.

126
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,041
Dad,

127
00:06:52,721 --> 00:06:55,520
I know you've never wanted me
involved in the projects.

128
00:06:56,361 --> 00:07:00,520
I can now publicly announce the news
about our cooperation with Shouke

129
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,640
and use the company's
stock price recovery

130
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,400
to reassure shareholders.

131
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:07,121
Or I can leave Jinda

132
00:07:08,001 --> 00:07:09,200
and work with Shouke alone.

133
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:14,001
Tell me your conditions.

134
00:07:16,601 --> 00:07:17,200
First,

135
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:20,200
I need to bring my own people
into the company.

136
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,640
Whatever department they go,

137
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:25,561
I want your decisive vote
supporting my choices.

138
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:26,320
Second,

139
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,280
I need to establish
my own independent department

140
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:31,200
with full authority
over personnel and financial matters,

141
00:07:31,361 --> 00:07:33,041
free from any interference.

142
00:07:34,241 --> 00:07:35,801
I hope to gain your support.

143
00:07:45,241 --> 00:07:46,440
All departments, get ready.

144
00:07:46,481 --> 00:07:47,320
Host, get ready.

145
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,400
Counting down.

146
00:07:48,561 --> 00:07:53,520
Five, four, three, two, one.

147
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:55,400
(Host: Xu Yan)
The city's renowned real estate firms,

148
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:59,001
Jinda Group and Shouke Real Estate,
have established strategic cooperation

149
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,601
in jointly developing Plot 178.

150
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:03,400
Both companies stated

151
00:08:03,481 --> 00:08:05,640
this marks a milestone collaboration,

152
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,161
signifying that both companies

153
00:08:07,241 --> 00:08:10,400
have taken solid steps
in diversified development strategies

154
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:14,440
while creating new opportunities
and growth potential for the industry.

155
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:18,520
Jinda Group will adopt Shouke's
technology and management expertise

156
00:08:18,801 --> 00:08:21,721
to further enhance project quality
and service standards

157
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:25,320
to provide consumers with quality,
convenient residential and commercial

158
00:08:25,361 --> 00:08:26,320
experiences.

159
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:30,320
(Reportedly, this cooperation
was spearheaded by Shen Haoming,)

160
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:33,921
(Jinda Group's Vice President
and head of the Plot 178 task force.)

161
00:08:34,561 --> 00:08:36,880
(He stated
that the successful agreement signing)

162
00:08:37,121 --> 00:08:39,921
(resulted from the company's
long-term commitment to innovation)

163
00:08:40,041 --> 00:08:41,520
(and deepened cooperation.)

164
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:44,520
(That concludes
the latest city updates.)

165
00:08:44,561 --> 00:08:47,121
(We'll continue
monitoring follow-up developments)

166
00:08:47,361 --> 00:08:50,561
(to bring you
more comprehensive coverage.)

167
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,681
Shen Jinsong

168
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,161
dares not face me.

169
00:08:58,041 --> 00:08:58,880
Shen Haoming,

170
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,760
you just rose to power

171
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,640
and are finding ways to sabotage me.

172
00:09:03,841 --> 00:09:05,280
First you promoted me sideways,

173
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:07,201
pushing me out of core departments

174
00:09:07,441 --> 00:09:08,560
and marginalizing me.

175
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,520
You really are something.

176
00:09:10,841 --> 00:09:12,680
I watched you grow up.

177
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:19,400
Is this how you
treat your father's key contributor?

178
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,601
There's no denying

179
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,880
you've brought the company
significant profits.

180
00:09:26,121 --> 00:09:27,760
But while generating revenue,

181
00:09:29,241 --> 00:09:30,880
plenty found its way into your pockets.

182
00:09:34,121 --> 00:09:35,201
You earn 3 million annually

183
00:09:36,241 --> 00:09:37,361
and own two villas,

184
00:09:37,441 --> 00:09:39,400
one with a 200-square-meter garden.

185
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,560
You also have

186
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:43,001
properties in America and Australia.

187
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,760
Over these years,

188
00:09:44,841 --> 00:09:46,680
you helped my father build this empire

189
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,121
as one of the founding pioneers.

190
00:09:49,241 --> 00:09:50,520
I've always respected you

191
00:09:51,081 --> 00:09:52,841
for your decades of dedication

192
00:09:52,841 --> 00:09:53,601
and hard work.

193
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:58,001
But your pay has been the highest
in the industry.

194
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,680
We haven't wronged you.

195
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,160
What I can do is

196
00:10:03,081 --> 00:10:05,040
when legal authorities prosecute you,

197
00:10:06,121 --> 00:10:09,361
I'll demonstrate to the court
about your cooperative attitude

198
00:10:09,361 --> 00:10:10,640
and your voluntary compensation.

199
00:10:13,241 --> 00:10:14,001
Stop thinking.

200
00:10:17,441 --> 00:10:18,841
This is your only option.

201
00:10:21,008 --> 00:10:22,512
(Resignation Agreement)

202
00:10:37,721 --> 00:10:38,520
What brings you?

203
00:10:39,961 --> 00:10:41,520
I knew you were working late.

204
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:44,361
So I wanted to ask you out
for late-night snacks.

205
00:10:45,601 --> 00:10:46,481
Since you mention it,

206
00:10:46,481 --> 00:10:47,520
I am actually hungry.

207
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,880
I just need to send an email.

208
00:10:49,241 --> 00:10:50,520
No problem, I'll wait.

209
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:52,640
Okay.

210
00:10:53,241 --> 00:10:53,841
Let's go.

211
00:10:55,601 --> 00:10:56,280
What to eat?

212
00:10:59,001 --> 00:11:00,081
That place from before?

213
00:11:00,321 --> 00:11:00,760
Okay.

214
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,441
Haoming.

215
00:11:04,441 --> 00:11:05,121
Mr. Wu.

216
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:07,201
Still working this late?

217
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:11,640
I need to talk with you.

218
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,001
Haoming, perhaps...

219
00:11:16,601 --> 00:11:17,201
Go ahead.

220
00:11:17,841 --> 00:11:19,400
I acknowledge my mistakes.

221
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:22,601
I accept the company's punishment.

222
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:27,201
But could you
consider my years of service

223
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,361
and give me one more chance?

224
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,001
I don't want to leave.

225
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,241
Mr. Wu,

226
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:38,920
you should've anticipated consequences
before acting.

227
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,280
Staying with the company is impossible.

228
00:11:41,961 --> 00:11:42,560
Let's go.

229
00:11:44,121 --> 00:11:44,760
Haoming,

230
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,361
my wife left me
and took the kids with her.

231
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:49,961
I got nothing in the divorce.

232
00:11:50,800 --> 00:11:51,920
Being fired at my age,

233
00:11:52,441 --> 00:11:53,400
if this gets out,

234
00:11:54,321 --> 00:11:55,321
I will be ruined

235
00:11:55,361 --> 00:11:57,160
and no company would ever hire me again.

236
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:00,121
Even my own wife and kids
look down on me.

237
00:12:02,481 --> 00:12:03,201
I'm sorry.

238
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:05,760
Haoming,

239
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,760
I've truly lost everything.

240
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,721
Please have some mercy

241
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,201
and let me stay in the company.

242
00:12:12,841 --> 00:12:15,920
Even a meaningless position would do.

243
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,961
I've truly lost everything.

244
00:12:21,201 --> 00:12:21,841
Mr. Wu,

245
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,680
consider it early retirement.

246
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,601
The company
can't make exceptions for this.

247
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:28,640
Let's go.

248
00:12:33,841 --> 00:12:34,481
Haoming.

249
00:12:36,241 --> 00:12:36,880
Haoming!

250
00:12:42,841 --> 00:12:43,481
Are you okay?

251
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,201
I'm fine.

252
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,241
Seems you really need to retire.

253
00:12:54,601 --> 00:12:55,481
Let me go!

254
00:12:56,601 --> 00:12:57,321
You alright?

255
00:13:15,344 --> 00:13:16,436
(Fang Lei)

256
00:13:43,441 --> 00:13:44,441
Back so early?

257
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:49,760
How's your injury?

258
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:52,040
I'm fine. Don't worry.

259
00:13:52,160 --> 00:13:52,800
Let me see.

260
00:13:55,241 --> 00:13:55,841
Haoming.

261
00:13:56,001 --> 00:14:00,201
I got you a supplementary card.

262
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:03,001
No spending limit. Use it freely.

263
00:14:06,321 --> 00:14:07,481
What's this reward for?

264
00:14:07,601 --> 00:14:10,081
Go shopping after you recover.

265
00:14:10,321 --> 00:14:11,481
Buy whatever you like.

266
00:14:13,481 --> 00:14:14,560
I don't want this.

267
00:14:15,001 --> 00:14:16,760
You must keep the card.

268
00:14:16,961 --> 00:14:17,400
Here.

269
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,560
There are more to come.

270
00:14:20,640 --> 00:14:21,920
That's not what I meant.

271
00:14:26,841 --> 00:14:27,321
Hello?

272
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:30,321
I see.

273
00:14:30,841 --> 00:14:31,640
I'm coming over now.

274
00:14:34,241 --> 00:14:35,201
It's about Wu Deliang.

275
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:36,721
I need to go to the office.

276
00:14:40,241 --> 00:14:41,361
Will you be back for dinner?

277
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,280
Sure.

278
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,400
Order takeout.

279
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:44,601
Don't cook yourself.

280
00:14:46,961 --> 00:14:47,961
I'll wait for you.

281
00:15:12,081 --> 00:15:12,601
Mr. Fang,

282
00:15:12,601 --> 00:15:13,680
long time no see.

283
00:15:14,520 --> 00:15:15,961
