572
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,441
go easy on your sister.

573
00:29:17,681 --> 00:29:18,280
No need.

574
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:20,840
We'll keep it fair since it's a match.

575
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:22,001
No advantages taken.

576
00:29:24,401 --> 00:29:25,441
Which club first?

577
00:29:26,280 --> 00:29:27,120
Iron club.

578
00:29:27,280 --> 00:29:28,441
That suits me better.

579
00:29:29,600 --> 00:29:30,320
I'll go first.

580
00:29:45,201 --> 00:29:45,800
Nice shot.

581
00:29:47,161 --> 00:29:47,800
Haoming,

582
00:29:48,201 --> 00:29:49,161
are you free tonight?

583
00:29:49,881 --> 00:29:52,001
Let me treat you and Yan to dinner.

584
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:54,641
I have a dinner
with Yuanhang Fund tonight.

585
00:29:56,320 --> 00:29:57,560
Why don't you join us?

586
00:29:58,441 --> 00:29:59,881
Mr. Yun, Mr. Liang,

587
00:30:00,001 --> 00:30:01,712
and their executive team
will be there too.

588
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,921
They might ask technical questions.

589
00:30:04,241 --> 00:30:05,320
We can play off each other.

590
00:30:06,560 --> 00:30:07,481
I'll follow your lead.

591
00:30:12,161 --> 00:30:13,840
Let's have dinner together tonight.

592
00:30:15,481 --> 00:30:17,001
I'll skip the work dinner.

593
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:17,840
Actually,

594
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:19,441
I'm having dinner with my cousin.

595
00:30:19,481 --> 00:30:19,921
Okay.

596
00:30:20,201 --> 00:30:21,120
Careful, it's hot.

597
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:22,641
How's the temperature?

598
00:30:22,921 --> 00:30:23,681
Just right.

599
00:30:28,280 --> 00:30:29,241
You've practiced a lot.

600
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:31,280
Not really.

601
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:34,040
Didn't you teach me everything I know?

602
00:30:34,280 --> 00:30:36,401
I never liked golfing in London.

603
00:30:38,201 --> 00:30:39,600
If you hadn't kept inviting me,

604
00:30:39,641 --> 00:30:40,800
I would've quit long ago.

605
00:30:41,001 --> 00:30:42,360
So thank you.

606
00:30:51,961 --> 00:30:52,760
No way.

607
00:30:52,840 --> 00:30:54,280
They could never be together.

608
00:30:54,961 --> 00:30:55,800
Keep your voice down.

609
00:30:57,961 --> 00:30:59,520
No matter what happens,

610
00:30:59,641 --> 00:31:01,800
he'd never fall for another woman.

611
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,241
Even if every man cheated,

612
00:31:03,241 --> 00:31:04,241
he wouldn't. Understand?

613
00:31:04,560 --> 00:31:06,001
You've only met him a few times.

614
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:08,201
Why trust him so much?

615
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:11,721
True, I haven't seen him often,

616
00:31:12,241 --> 00:31:14,080
but I observe carefully each time

617
00:31:14,481 --> 00:31:15,481
and see it clearly.

618
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:18,280
Every second, he only has eyes for you.

619
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:27,001
But we used to share everything.

620
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:35,721
Now it feels like glass separates us.

621
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:38,040
We can see each other,

622
00:31:39,681 --> 00:31:41,080
but can't get closer.

623
00:31:43,161 --> 00:31:45,161
Maybe you're overthinking?

624
00:31:45,481 --> 00:31:47,721
Look, he's a businessman

625
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:49,360
working around clock.

626
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:51,161
Maybe he's just tired.

627
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:52,401
Right?

628
00:31:53,921 --> 00:31:55,760
We finally got together today.

629
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:56,280
Forget him.

630
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:56,840
Let's drink.

631
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:09,921
Haoming,

632
00:32:10,840 --> 00:32:12,520
don't you think I'm great?

633
00:32:13,201 --> 00:32:17,641
Today I finally got Jiang Yun
and Jiang Liang into signing for you.

634
00:32:18,441 --> 00:32:20,560
Our efforts finally paid off.

635
00:32:21,441 --> 00:32:22,120
You did great.

636
00:32:22,560 --> 00:32:23,840
You acted very professionally.

637
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:26,320
Well done.

638
00:32:26,881 --> 00:32:27,840
I'll get you some water.

639
00:32:34,320 --> 00:32:35,161
Haoming,

640
00:32:36,921 --> 00:32:38,201
take a good look at me.

641
00:32:43,241 --> 00:32:44,481
I grew up long ago.

642
00:32:50,896 --> 00:32:52,336
(Yan)

643
00:33:09,264 --> 00:33:10,288
(Chen Lin)

644
00:33:15,481 --> 00:33:16,760
Can you not answer that?

645
00:33:17,721 --> 00:33:18,320
It's Chen Lin.

646
00:33:20,401 --> 00:33:21,280
Then answer it.

647
00:33:24,840 --> 00:33:25,401
Hello?

648
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:27,441
It's done.

649
00:33:28,201 --> 00:33:28,681
The photo

650
00:33:28,760 --> 00:33:29,560
is sent to you.

651
00:33:29,760 --> 00:33:30,201
Okay.

652
00:33:44,181 --> 00:33:45,680
(Signatures)

653
00:33:47,921 --> 00:33:49,360
Why show me this?

654
00:33:49,721 --> 00:33:50,961
Mr. Huang and your father

655
00:33:51,441 --> 00:33:52,840
just signed the contract in the US.

656
00:33:53,721 --> 00:33:55,481
Good thing your father is on my side.

657
00:33:56,280 --> 00:33:58,441
Or the New District project
wouldn't materialize.

658
00:34:00,961 --> 00:34:03,241
Well he's my father.

659
00:34:03,441 --> 00:34:04,721
Naturally he supports

660
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:07,840
the person I like.

661
00:34:12,641 --> 00:34:13,961
Thank him for me.

662
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:15,840
Get some rest early.

663
00:34:16,961 --> 00:34:17,881
Shen Haoming,

664
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:19,481
what are you doing?

665
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:25,201
Now it's truly settled.

666
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:27,280
You performed excellently.

667
00:34:28,120 --> 00:34:31,080
You'll be very pleased
with this year's bonus.

668
00:34:31,721 --> 00:34:32,360
Stop.

669
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:37,420
Were you nice to me

670
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:41,200
just to win over my father

671
00:34:42,200 --> 00:34:43,281
and keep me in check?

672
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:50,600
You've been putting on an act with me.

673
00:34:52,001 --> 00:34:53,321
Can't call it an act.

674
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:55,801
Just to keep you stable

675
00:34:57,361 --> 00:34:58,881
and prevent your occasional outbursts.

676
00:35:00,040 --> 00:35:00,841
Shen Haoming!

677
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:02,040
I love you so much.

678
00:35:02,481 --> 00:35:03,720
You think I'm a lunatic?

679
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:05,321
I'll tell Xu Yan

680
00:35:05,680 --> 00:35:06,441
and my father

681
00:35:06,441 --> 00:35:07,361
about what you've done.

682
00:35:08,720 --> 00:35:09,401
Suit yourself.

683
00:35:10,801 --> 00:35:12,040
If you dare walk out that door,

684
00:35:12,120 --> 00:35:13,520
I won't let you off.

685
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:16,841
I'm begging you, Haoming.

686
00:35:17,001 --> 00:35:18,080
I didn't mean to.

687
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,240
Don't be angry.

688
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,080
Mr. Shen.

689
00:35:24,841 --> 00:35:25,321
Han Weiping,

690
00:35:25,321 --> 00:35:26,200
why are you here?

691
00:35:26,680 --> 00:35:27,881
Let me reintroduce you.

692
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:29,520
Han Weiping,

693
00:35:30,441 --> 00:35:33,441
former senior corporate lawyer
at Jinda Group,

694
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,520
now my private attorney.

695
00:35:36,921 --> 00:35:38,001
You've worked hard lately.

696
00:35:38,361 --> 00:35:39,881
Take your time with the follow-ups.

697
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:40,801
Don't worry.

698
00:35:40,881 --> 00:35:41,841
I'll handle it properly.

699
00:35:42,001 --> 00:35:43,040
What do you mean?

700
00:35:43,481 --> 00:35:44,600
Why did you lie to me?

701
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:46,080
Explain yourself.

702
00:35:47,240 --> 00:35:48,200
Go away.

703
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:49,401
Go!

704
00:35:51,881 --> 00:35:52,761
Had enough drama?

705
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:55,160
You...

706
00:35:55,841 --> 00:35:57,481
All of you are liars.

707
00:35:58,520 --> 00:36:00,720
It was all a setup from the beginning.

708
00:36:00,761 --> 00:36:01,801
You trapped me.

709
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:05,720
You think signing means victory?

710
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:07,761
I won't forgive any of you.

711
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,640
Especially you, Han Weiping.

712
00:36:10,001 --> 00:36:10,680
Miss Fang,

713
00:36:11,401 --> 00:36:12,801
as a professional lawyer,

714
00:36:13,321 --> 00:36:14,881
I advise against escalating conflicts.

715
00:36:15,881 --> 00:36:16,680
What?

716
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:18,640
Scared now?

717
00:36:19,240 --> 00:36:20,080
I'm not scared.

718
00:36:20,801 --> 00:36:21,921
I want to tell you.

719
00:36:22,321 --> 00:36:23,801
You tried to wreck Mr. Shen's family.

720
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:25,200
For every thing you did

721
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:26,160
and every word you said,

722
00:36:26,881 --> 00:36:29,600
I have all evidence and recordings.

723
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:35,600
So I advise you.

724
00:36:35,961 --> 00:36:37,001
You're still young.

725
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:40,120
You need reputation
for future endeavors.

726
00:36:51,921 --> 00:36:53,240
You were my client after all.

727
00:36:53,841 --> 00:36:54,961
I'll let it slide this time.

728
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:56,520
If there's a next time,

729
00:36:57,080 --> 00:36:58,441
you'll face legal consequences.

730
00:36:58,761 --> 00:36:59,640
Get some rest.

731
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:43,481
It's late.

732
00:37:43,921 --> 00:37:44,680
Still awake?

733
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:53,841
I'm expecting you.

734
00:37:56,401 --> 00:37:57,720
Why didn't you answer your phone?

735
00:37:59,321 --> 00:38:00,961
I had something important to handle.

736
00:38:01,761 --> 00:38:03,120
So I didn't call back. Sorry.

737
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:12,160
Haoming,

738
00:38:14,841 --> 00:38:16,281
I need to tell you something.

739
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:22,240
If it's something that'll make me happy,

740
00:38:22,761 --> 00:38:23,560
go ahead and say it.

741
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:29,361
If it'll upset me,

742
00:38:33,321 --> 00:38:34,640
don't say a single word.

743
00:38:39,801 --> 00:38:40,761
I'm a bit tired.

744
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:42,441
I need to rest.

745
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:39,401
Yan.

746
00:39:45,881 --> 00:39:46,680
Why are you here?

747
00:39:48,921 --> 00:39:50,160
I'm here to pick up Haochen.

748
00:39:50,321 --> 00:39:51,801
Why are you picking up Haochen?

749
00:39:53,520 --> 00:39:54,600
Does this need a reason?

750
00:39:56,921 --> 00:39:58,200
I'm his biological aunt.

751
00:40:04,441 --> 00:40:05,801
What scheme are you plotting now?

752
00:40:07,761 --> 00:40:08,680
This is a school.

753
00:40:10,441 --> 00:40:11,640
Control yourself and leave.

754
00:40:12,361 --> 00:40:13,040
Yan,

755
00:40:15,361 --> 00:40:17,001
actually, every time I face you,

756
00:40:18,281 --> 00:40:20,080
I feel really guilty inside.

757
00:40:21,401 --> 00:40:22,520
Also, I found out

758
00:40:23,001 --> 00:40:24,600
you've been kept in the dark.

759
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:27,001
I think this situation

760
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,560
is very unfair to you.

761
00:40:30,600 --> 00:40:34,881
Actually, Haoming and Haochen
aren't brothers at all.

762
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:38,401
They're father and son.

763
00:40:48,801 --> 00:40:50,881
When Haoming was studying in London,

764
00:40:51,401 --> 00:40:52,520
he dated my sister.

765
00:40:53,160 --> 00:40:55,640
My sister got accidentally pregnant
and gave birth to Haochen.

766
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:58,441
But they were still young back then,

767
00:40:58,600 --> 00:40:59,600
only twenty years old.

768
00:41:00,281 --> 00:41:02,401
My sister made me keep it
from our father.

769
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:07,560
So the baby was taken
by the Shens immediately after birth.

770
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:13,321
Shen Jinsong and Yu Lan were worried
about an illegitimate child scandal.

771
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:15,961
Fortunately, not many people
knew about it.

772
00:41:16,481 --> 00:41:18,641
To the public, they said

773
00:41:19,664 --> 00:41:21,321
(it's Haoming's younger brother.)

774
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:26,961
Later, my sister died
in a diving accident.

775
00:41:28,961 --> 00:41:32,441
That made this matter
a permanent secret.

776
00:41:40,841 --> 00:41:43,881
The three of us are blood-related.

777
00:41:44,321 --> 00:41:45,600
No one can change that

778
00:41:45,640 --> 00:41:46,961
or sever that bond.

779
00:41:47,481 --> 00:41:48,560
In this world,

780
00:41:48,761 --> 00:41:52,040
no one could accept Haochen
more sincerely than me.

781
00:41:57,281 --> 00:41:58,640
You probably didn't know this.

782
00:41:59,040 --> 00:42:00,281
On your birthday,

783
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,321
Haoming was at my place.

784
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:07,321
You didn't answer my call.

785
00:42:07,321 --> 00:42:08,640
I feared something happened.

786
00:42:08,841 --> 00:42:09,361
I'm fine.

787
00:42:09,921 --> 00:42:11,881
Shifeng and Jinda
are signing an agreement.

788
00:42:11,961 --> 00:42:12,921
We had a meeting.

789
00:42:13,281 --> 00:42:14,680
So I put my phone on silent.

790
00:42:16,761 --> 00:42:18,281
He probably didn't tell you

791
00:42:18,520 --> 00:42:20,520
what we did together, did he?

792
00:42:35,481 --> 00:42:37,481
Unless Shen Haoming tells me himself,

793
00:42:40,240 --> 00:42:41,680
I won't believe anything you say.

794
00:42:43,761 --> 00:42:45,841
You... you don't think

795
00:42:45,921 --> 00:42:51,040
your relationship with Haoming
is some pure romance, do you?

796
00:42:59,441 --> 00:43:01,600
From the start,
he wasn't looking for a wife.

797
00:43:01,801 --> 00:43:05,640
He wanted a name
to put on a marriage certificate.

798
00:43:07,120 --> 00:43:09,130
You just happened to appear

799
00:43:09,130 --> 00:43:11,001
(in his sight at that time.)

800
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:13,080
But my philosophy is

801
00:43:14,921 --> 00:43:17,321
I must shape it into what I like.

802
00:43:22,801 --> 00:43:24,441
You're not from matching social status,

803
00:43:26,120 --> 00:43:27,401
but you're fairly clever

804
00:43:27,961 --> 00:43:28,921
and ambitious.

805
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:31,080
You've become a host lately,

806
00:43:31,401 --> 00:43:33,761
which perfectly serves
to promote his business

807
00:43:33,921 --> 00:43:34,761
and his character.

808
00:43:35,361 --> 00:43:38,600
I wonder if we could have the honor
of Xu Yan interviewing you.

809
00:43:40,680 --> 00:43:42,921
Consider it
giving the new host a chance.

810
00:43:49,321 --> 00:43:51,200
A seemingly perfect family

811
00:43:51,761 --> 00:43:54,841
can gain him much trust
from business partners.

812
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:58,401
Plus you're obedient and sensible.

813
00:43:59,520 --> 00:44:01,281
Even knowing he has a child,

814
00:44:02,240 --> 00:44:03,881
you'd still let him control you.

815
00:44:05,001 --> 00:44:08,361
It'd be a perfect
and rational choice for him.

816
00:44:10,401 --> 00:44:11,040
By the way,

817
00:44:12,361 --> 00:44:16,921
you actually thought you became a host
through your own ability?

818
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:20,001
He put in great effort

819
00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:21,921
to get you that host position.

820
00:44:33,489 --> 00:44:34,896
Bye bye!

821
00:44:34,896 --> 00:44:36,987
- Bye.
- Bye, sir!

822
00:44:41,961 --> 00:44:42,640
Sis-in-law?

823
00:44:44,361 --> 00:44:45,321
Sis-in-law.

824
00:44:53,761 --> 00:44:55,001
(Haochen is your brother.)

825
00:44:55,160 --> 00:44:56,361
(We're family.)

826
00:44:56,720 --> 00:44:59,520
(It's only natural for us
to care for each other.)

827
00:44:59,640 --> 00:45:00,961
(You've done well.)

828
00:45:01,160 --> 00:45:02,401
Thank you, sis-in-law.

829
00:45:07,720 --> 00:45:10,801
(Haochen has been spoiled
ever since he was born.)

830
00:45:11,200 --> 00:45:13,040
(His temper grew worse and worse.)

831
00:45:13,281 --> 00:45:16,720
(I never expected
you'd get along so well with him.)

832
00:45:17,560 --> 00:45:19,961
(I think he genuinely likes you.)

833
00:45:28,464 --> 00:45:30,380
♪Like fireworks that loved♪

834
00:45:30,380 --> 00:45:32,039
♪Rushing toward the stars♪

835
00:45:32,039 --> 00:45:34,098
♪Undaunted by pain♪

836
00:45:34,941 --> 00:45:36,842
♪Fearless of flames♪

837
00:45:36,842 --> 00:45:40,496
♪Even if just a fleeting sparkle♪

838
00:45:41,501 --> 00:45:43,325
♪We shed tears♪

839
00:45:43,421 --> 00:45:47,173
♪Deep blue seas turn to foam♪

840
00:45:47,173 --> 00:45:51,024
♪We regained freedom♪

841
00:45:51,024 --> 00:45:53,753
♪If you remember me♪

842
00:45:53,753 --> 00:45:56,592
♪Then I'm pleased♪

843
00:46:09,737 --> 00:46:13,881
♪I just wanna take my time tonight♪

844
00:46:15,882 --> 00:46:20,172
♪To do all the things I said I'd try♪

845
00:46:21,897 --> 00:46:27,753
♪I go surfing, go diving, go driving,
and go flying to a different place♪

846
00:46:28,233 --> 00:46:31,049
♪I go drink, go party, and go dance♪

847
00:46:31,049 --> 00:46:34,377
♪Even if I'm lonely♪

848
00:46:35,017 --> 00:46:39,753
♪Cause I just have been hurt
too many times♪

849
00:46:41,525 --> 00:46:45,763
♪I'm giving it all to get nothing back♪

850
00:46:47,625 --> 00:46:52,777
♪I was lost in the dark,
and it's too hurt to even see♪

